info.author: Giannis Korontanis
info.name: converter-package
info.summary: Converter is a reasoning tool designed for the cloud language known as CEAML. CEAML is an extension of TOSCA capable to describe deployment and runtime adaptation for platforms that utilize both Cloud and Edge resources. It can parse CEAML entities and translate them into configuration files for K3s or Kubevirt.
